# XcodeBuildMCP — Required Tooling

For **all** build / test / run / debug / simulator tasks in this Apple platform project:

1. Read `.cursor/skills/xcodebuildmcp/SKILL.md` at the start of any build/run session.
2. Always call `session_show_defaults` before the first build, run, or test action — never skip.
3. Use XcodeBuildMCP MCP tools instead of raw shell calls (`xcodebuild`, `xcrun`, `simctl`).

Key commands per AGENTS.md:
- Build: `xcodebuild -project VideoPlayer.xcodeproj -scheme VideoPlayer build`
- Test:  `xcodebuild -project VideoPlayer.xcodeproj -scheme VideoPlayer test`

Do not proceed or commit if the build fails.
